CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 21, 1956, page A1, reads: "OES Committee for the grand affair held during the 39th annual session of Deborah Grand Chapter OES PHA, included, front, Ruth Tucker, Charles Jones, Ella Mae Phillips. Rear: Vera Winslow, Virginia Valentine and Juanita Saunders. - 'Teenie' Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of the OES Committee, left to right, front row: Ruth Tucker wearing striped sash, Charles Jones wearing tuxedo, Ella Mae Phillips; rear row: Vera Winslow, Virginia Valentine, and Juanita Saunders, wearing light colored dresses and ribbons, posed in front of stairs for the 39th annual session of Deborah Grand Chapter OES PHA
